<html>
  <h1> Bacon, Egg, and Cheese Sandwich </h1>
   <h2> By Corey Taylor </h2>
  <p> I used to make this a lot because, in high school, I worked at Waffle House. Prior to that, I used to never eat breakfast </p>
  
  <h3> Ingredients </h3>
  <p>Bacon 
    <br/> Cheese
    <br/> Egg
    <br/> Bread
    <br/> Butter
  </p>
  
  <h3> What to do </h3>
  
  <p> Step 1: Spread butter on backside of bread and then place on stove (or alternative method of heating).
  <br/>
    Step 2: Place preferred cheese on slice of bread, along with bacon.
 <br/>
    Step 3:Wait for cheese to melt and wait for bread to get as toasted as desired.
  
  </p>
  
  
</html>
